First install OpenNINITE
	Unzip the file
	In Terminal, type cd and drag the unzipped file into Terminal. Hit return.
	Type sudo ./install.sh to run the installer

Second install SimpleOpenNI by unzipping it and copying it into your libraries folder in Processing. Restart Processing.

*This program is using a second USB web cam for the RGB image. Make sure you have a second camera plugged in.